menu "BadgeLink"

    config BADGELINK_QUEUE_SIZE
        int "RX queue size (number of fragments)"
        default 256
        range 16 1024
        help
            Size of the receive queue for BadgeLink fragments.
            Each fragment is 32 bytes. Larger values use more memory
            but can handle higher throughput.

    config BADGELINK_HOST_TANMATSU_LAUNCHER
        bool "Host application is the Tanmatsu launcher"
        default n
        help
            Enable when BadgeLink is built as part of the Tanmatsu launcher
            firmware. When set, the start-app handler calls the launcher's
            prepare_device_for_app_launch() hook before booting the selected
            AppFS slot, so the device is left in a known state (USB in
            flash/monitor mode, radio powered off) before handing control to
            the launched app.

endmenu
